<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>zf create controller creates a controller file where the leading slash is missing on the extends section.</p>

<p>i.e. it creates:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
namespace Core;

class IndexController extends Zend\Controller\Action
{
</code></pre>

<p>and should be:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
namespace Core;

class IndexController extends \Zend\Controller\Action
{
</code></pre>

